                            ref="#places/84"
                            key="#Cities #Fiscal_property #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            >Salerno</placeName>) omnis rebus, qui fuit ipsius <name
                            ref="Maurus Iohannes">Mauri Iohanni</name> filio eius, qui <rs
                            key="#Property_of_persons_without_heirs">sine heredibus defuncti
                            fuerunt</rs>… </ab>
